include Directory Reference

Files

file  aes.h
 This is the AES module header file for the register level AES driver. It defines various encryption modes supported by the AES module.
 
file  crypto_internal.h
 This is the internal Header for the Crypto Driver. This header file should NOT be directly included by applications.
 
file  hmac.h
 This is the HMAC module header file for the register level HMAC driver.
 
file  reg_aes.h
 This file gives register definitions of MSS_AES module.
 
file  reg_dthe.h
 This file gives register definitions of MSS_DTHE module.
 
file  reg_pka.h
 This file gives register definitions of MSS_PKA module.
 
file  reg_sha.h
 This file gives register definitions of MSS_SHA module.
 
file  reg_trng.h
 This file gives register definitions of MSS_TRNG module.
